
A simple command-line to-do list application that allows add, list, update, and delete tasks.
Commands:
add: Add a new task.
list: List all tasks.
update: Update an existing task.
delete: Delete a task.
python todo.py add "Buy" -d ".1.1." -due date
python todo.py list
python todo.py update 1 -t "G" -s completed
python todo.py delete 1
